>> A-Z and [[:space:]] are OK too.
> 
> The 'i' at the end of the regex means case-insensitive ;) but yes, I 
> forgot whitespace. So something like:
> 
>   if ($name =~ /[^a-z0-9[:space:]]/i) {
>     quote_name;
>   }
> 
>> I skimmed the spec, but nothing jumped out at me.
> 
